      <h1>Why Customer Testimonial Videos Are a Game Changer</h1>
      <p class="lead">Discover how customer testimonial videos build trust, boost engagement, and help brands connect with the right audience.</p>
      <p class="post-meta"><span>Sofia Treviño</span> <span>·</span> <span>November 1, 2024</span> <span>·</span> <span>Updated March 18, 2025</span></p>
