<!-- ============ ARTICLE ============ -->
<section class="sec" style="padding-top:40px">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="post-wrap post-body reveal">
<p>Customer testimonial videos are a game changer because they let real customers make the case for a brand, which lands as more credible than any ad. Siemens Switzerland saw a 3x increase in engagement after featuring authentic employee and customer testimonials, and companies like Meteomatics and SV Group have used the same approach to strengthen trust and expand their reach.</p><h2>The Power of Authenticity</h2><p>In a world where audiences are constantly bombarded by advertisements, real stories from real customers are far harder to tune out. <a href={p("services/brand-video")}>Customer testimonial videos</a> show the human side of a brand rather than simply telling people it's great.</p><p>Siemens Switzerland worked with Viven to create videos that showcase its culture, its people, and why it's a great place to work. Through these authentic testimonials, Siemens saw a 3x increase in engagement, helping it connect with both current and future employees — one of the case studies featured in our <a href={p("projects")}>portfolio</a>.</p><h2>Why Testimonials Cut Through the Noise</h2><p>People have become experts at tuning out ads, but a real story from a real customer is far harder to ignore. That's the core reason testimonial videos consistently outperform brand-authored messaging: the audience is hearing from someone who has already made the decision they're weighing.</p><h2>How Customer Testimonial Videos Can Drive Real Results</h2><p>Meteomatics, a weather data solutions company, needed a way to make complex technical data more approachable and relatable. By featuring real customers in testimonial videos, Viven helped tell the story of how the product makes lives easier — strengthening the brand, expanding its reach, and bringing in more customers.</p><h2>Why Viven's Testimonial Videos Work</h2><p>Viven specializes in helping brands tell authentic stories: the most compelling marketing comes from real people, and knowing how to bring those stories to life is what makes them resonate. Whether it's building trust, showcasing company culture, or highlighting a product's real-world impact, brands like SV Group have used this approach to create a lasting impression — a trend explored further in <a href={p("blog/testimonials-the-most-trusted-marketing-tool-in-2025")}>testimonials: the most trusted marketing tool in 2025</a> and <a href={p("blog/how-brands-build-trust-and-credibility-through-video")}>how brands build trust and credibility through video</a>.</p><h2>Where Testimonial Videos Fit in a Marketing Mix</h2><p>Testimonial videos work best alongside other formats rather than in isolation — pairing them with product or brand videos gives prospects both the emotional proof and the practical detail they need to decide.</p><h2>Ready to Tell Your Brand's Story?</h2><p>If you want to build real connections with your audience, there's no better way than through customer testimonial videos. <a href={p("contact")}>Let's chat about how we can help you tell your brand's authentic story.</a></p>
    </div>
    <p class="post-service-note"><a href={p("services/brand-video")}>Want to see how this works in practice? Explore our brand video production.</a></p>
